{"tid":659704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再失7.1維園檔期 民陣︰東角道見","createTime":"2018-05-10T05:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T07:44:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8784a2ffbdccd1ad8b79df326f40fc88d792d3f","tid":659704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180510/20386258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20386258&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FEV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d2679587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20386258&h=35b4a55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180510/20386258</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月10日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：再失7.1維園檔期<br />\n民陣︰東角道見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180510/large/18164752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180510%2Flarge%2F18164752.jpg&h=a14ef763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年慶委會以慈善團體名義，成功攞快證訂咗維園足球場嘅7.1檔期。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n親共團體香港各界慶典委員會舊年以慈善團體名義，成功攞快證訂咗維園足球場嘅7.1檔期。今年佢哋食過翻尋味，又再重施故技，搶咗今年7.1維園足球場檔期，又再令到主辦7.1遊行嘅民陣食白果。民陣警權關注組召集人區諾軒話，今年大家可能要喺銅鑼灣東角道起步喇。<br />\n<br />\n舊年慶委會話7.1要喺維園搞創科展覽，而康文署就話民陣遲咗申請，加上慶委會係法例下嘅慈善團體，所以享有優先權獲批場地，結果民陣要用維園草地起步。<br />\n<br />\n今年民陣又再入紙申請，但又俾各界慶典委員會搶咗個場，區諾軒仲話，民陣連維園草地都唔會申請㗎喇。既然建制派要咁玩法，咁佢哋都應該「pay the price（付出代價）」，於是民陣就申請用東角道做遊行起步點囉，仲要係申請1,500人嘅遊行。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人葉志衍就解釋，想遊行嘅市民根本唔想入草地等，而且舊年落雨，喺草地等就更唔理想。葉志衍仲話，原本約咗昨日同警方傾，不過警方取消咗個會，惟有等下次。其實個制度一日冇變，慶委會用慈善團體身份同民陣搶，民陣都申請唔到，各界慶典委員會就可以永續用維園嘅。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：北角街坊會搞八段錦App　創科基金批出四球 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)"},{"pid":"df75a0865f0641d6c90bdbdced4451c33bdaaf18","tid":659704,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f59b79c240b2513e49cc7b25b1c311e6ef591a65","tid":659704,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"大把傻仔去 放心"},{"pid":"63f27b6ba80d2ff6014349168d558fbc942cde22","tid":659704,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6f42a946c8ff4776d441d08746d281f5d8e5e83","tid":659704,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"東華3院籌款活動上線啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341cac6665196641fe16e55ef10773779b917acf","tid":659704,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f27ef8f4b5c27de5211b2929119cd90f4721267","tid":659704,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">含撚泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/153743_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F153743_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=330fdcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9f3a67c66bee7500da0dac60c1888503f46b659d","tid":659704,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"人地唔俾就轉場，抗爭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6bddffaab357e8d0e1c13844a6823322b7fe62","tid":659704,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"我要去愛國遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"